{"type": "article", "id": 15082, "title": "“poets” 石墨与玻璃系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-18T07:26:29Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 12, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606000339lj1nzVeOXgd6A2IL.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t“poets” 系列原本是玻璃手工大师 Massimo Lunardo 邀请多位艺术家共同打造的玻璃制品，展现玻璃不完美的状态。在今年的装博会上展出时，不仅增加了设计师，还增加了石墨元素。或是在玻璃罩之外做一个石墨把手，或是在玻璃瓶外加一个石墨的支撑底座。黑色的不透明的石墨很难做出艺术感，与玻璃恰好构成反差，巧妙的使用往往能成为点睛之笔，也是设计师的新挑战。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142415yKGnXaqYM3xwcZQL.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"524\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6405868\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142416kqdfom7ZyiWeMND1.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"550\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67237164\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142416MiKtoky7qCYhp6j8.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"477\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.58312958\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726142416s8YXkmNyF92Vvbaz.jpg\" width=\"818\" height=\"477\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.58312958\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}